Example: char ch = getchar(); putchar(ch);

b) Formatted I/O functions: printf(), scanf()
Example: printf("%d",x); scanf("%d",&x);

c) Non-formatted I/O functions: fread(), fwrite() for file I/O
Example: fread(&var, sizeof(var), 1, fp);

